{% doc %}
  @prompt
    
    **Prompt:**
    
    Build me a custom Shopify theme section called "Hero - Image & Video" as a fully self-contained `.liquid` file. This is a hero section with the following requirements:
    
    **Core behavior:**
    - On desktop, the background is a **static image**
    - On mobile, the background is a **video** (autoplay, muted, loop, playsinline)
    - Both swap cleanly at a breakpoint of 768px using CSS only — no JavaScript required for the swap
    - The section should stack content (text, buttons) centered over the background media
    
    **Schema settings — everything must be editable in the Shopify theme customizer with no URL pasting:**
    
    For the image:
    - Image picker (uses Shopify's native `type: image_picker` so the merchant uploads directly from their Shopify Files or media library — no URL field)
    - Aspect ratio selector for desktop image with options: 16:9, 4:3, 21:9, 1:1, and a "natural" option that follows the image's own ratio
    - Object fit setting: Cover or Contain
    
    For the video:
    - Video picker (uses Shopify's native `type: video` so the merchant uploads directly from Shopify Files — no URL field)
    - Aspect ratio selector for mobile video with the same ratio options: 9:16, 4:5, 1:1, 16:9
    - The video must use the `{{ section.settings.video }}` Shopify video object and render via the `video_tag` filter
    
    **Hero content (all editable in customizer):**
    - Heading text with font size control (small/medium/large/xl)
    - Subheading text
    - Two CTA buttons — each with editable label, link, and style toggle (filled or outlined)
    - Text color picker
    - Text alignment: left, center, right
    - Overlay opacity slider (0–100%) with a color picker for overlay color so text stays readable over any background
    
    **Section-level controls:**
    - Desktop section height: auto (follows aspect ratio) or fixed height in px
    - Mobile section height: same options
    - Padding top and padding bottom controls
    
    **Technical requirements:**
    - All styles scoped to the section ID so nothing bleeds into other sections
    - Use CSS custom properties for aspect ratios set inline via `style` attribute on the wrapper, driven by the schema settings
    - The image and video swap must be handled purely with a CSS media query — hide the image on mobile, hide the video on desktop
    - Clean, well-commented code throughout
    - Schema must be complete and valid with proper `default` values for every setting so the section looks good on first drop with no configuration
    
    Output the complete `.liquid` file ready to upload to my Shopify theme.
    
    ---
    
    This gives any AI coding tool everything it needs to build it right the first time., Right now, the section goes way below the video, even though I have it selected so that it should be the fixed height with the correct aspect ratio. There is also a bunch of random letters and numbers below the video that need to be gone. 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% liquid
  assign desktop_aspect_ratio = block.settings.desktop_aspect_ratio
  assign mobile_aspect_ratio = block.settings.mobile_aspect_ratio
  
  case desktop_aspect_ratio
    when '16:9'
      assign desktop_ratio_value = '56.25%'
    when '4:3'
      assign desktop_ratio_value = '75%'
    when '21:9'
      assign desktop_ratio_value = '42.86%'
    when '1:1'
      assign desktop_ratio_value = '100%'
    when 'natural'
      assign desktop_ratio_value = 'auto'
  endcase
  
  case mobile_aspect_ratio
    when '9:16'
      assign mobile_ratio_value = '177.78%'
    when '4:5'
      assign mobile_ratio_value = '125%'
    when '1:1'
      assign mobile_ratio_value = '100%'
    when '16:9'
      assign mobile_ratio_value = '56.25%'
  endcase
  
  assign desktop_height_mode = block.settings.desktop_height_mode
  assign mobile_height_mode = block.settings.mobile_height_mode
%}

{% style %}
  .ai-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    {% if desktop_height_mode == 'auto' %}
      {% if desktop_aspect_ratio == 'natural' %}
        height: auto;
      {% else %}
        padding-bottom: {{ desktop_ratio_value }};
        height: 0;
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
      height: {{ block.settings.desktop_height_px }}px;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-hero-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.object_fit }};
  }

  .ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-hero-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} video {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.object_fit }};
  }

  .ai-hero-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
    opacity: {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 800px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
    z-index: 2;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    {% case block.settings.heading_size %}
      {% when 'small' %}
        font-size: 32px;
        line-height: 1.2;
      {% when 'medium' %}
        font-size: 48px;
        line-height: 1.1;
      {% when 'large' %}
        font-size: 64px;
        line-height: 1.1;
      {% when 'xl' %}
        font-size: 80px;
        line-height: 1;
    {% endcase %}
  }

  .ai-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.text_alignment == 'right' %}
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% else %}
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% endif %}
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-hero-button-filled-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-filled-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-outlined-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-outlined-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
    .ai-hero-media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if mobile_height_mode == 'auto' %}
        padding-bottom: {{ mobile_ratio_value }};
        height: 0;
      {% else %}
        height: {{ block.settings.mobile_height_px }}px;
        padding-bottom: 0;
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: none;
    }

    .ai-hero-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
    }

    .ai-hero-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% case block.settings.heading_size %}
        {% when 'small' %}
          font-size: 24px;
        {% when 'medium' %}
          font-size: 32px;
        {% when 'large' %}
          font-size: 40px;
        {% when 'xl' %}
          font-size: 48px;
      {% endcase %}
    }

    .ai-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .ai-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-hero-media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.desktop_image %}
      <img
        src="{{ block.settings.desktop_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}"
        alt="{{ block.settings.desktop_image.alt | escape }}"
        loading="lazy"
        width="{{ block.settings.desktop_image.width }}"
        height="{{ block.settings.desktop_image.height }}"
        class="ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
      >
    {% else %}
      <div class="ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: #f4f4f4;"></div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.mobile_video %}
      <div class="ai-hero-video-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.mobile_video | video_tag: autoplay: true, loop: true, muted: true, playsinline: true, controls: false }}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="ai-hero-video-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: #333;"></div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-hero-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>

    <div class="ai-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
        <h1 class="ai-hero-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h1>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.subheading != blank %}
        <p class="ai-hero-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</p>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.button_1_label != blank or block.settings.button_2_label != blank %}
        <div class="ai-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.button_1_label != blank %}
            <a 
              href="{{ block.settings.button_1_link }}" 
              class="ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% if block.settings.button_1_style == 'filled' %}ai-hero-button-filled-{{ ai_gen_id }}{% else %}ai-hero-button-outlined-{{ ai_gen_id }}{% endif %}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.button_1_label }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.button_2_label != blank %}
            <a 
              href="{{ block.settings.button_2_link }}" 
              class="ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% if block.settings.button_2_style == 'filled' %}ai-hero-button-filled-{{ ai_gen_id }}{% else %}ai-hero-button-outlined-{{ ai_gen_id }}{% endif %}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.button_2_label }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

